name: Get 11+
description:
Get 11+ is a number puzzle game. It's easy to start, but it's hard to get 11+. Just enjoy this funny game!

Easy to play:
Click the tiles with same number, and they will pop up. Click again to merge them together. Enjoy it and try to get 11+!

Features:
· Simple and beautiful design.
· Allow to submit high score to Game Center.
· Share your score with your friends via Facebook.
